    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 145</em>, <em>Ultimate Combat pg. 142</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> strong enchantment <strong>CL</strong> 12th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> weapon quality; <strong>Price</strong> +3 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can only be placed on one-handed or two-handed firearms. A <em>greater lucky </em>firearm is nearly identical to a <em>lucky </em>firearm, but its reservoir holds 3 grit points instead of 1. A firearm cannot have both this special ability and the <em>lucky </em>special ability.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>greater heroism</em>, creator must be a grit user; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
